	 ('A Peace of My Mind Keynote','Come join our community in attending John Noltner’s (A Peace of My Mind) keynote presentation at 7:30 pm on Monday, April 7th in the Paulus Lecture Hall, located in the law school building. Featuring John’s own story and a presentation of portraits featuring members of the Willamette community, it will be a night of storytelling you won’t want to miss!','A multi-media keynote presentation by A Peace of My Mind shares John’s own story of following his passion, while at the same time revealing the wisdom of everyday Americans and their stories of hope, transformation, and forgiveness. With black-white portraits John captures and personal stories shared, ordinary people reveal extraordinary insights into how we can work toward common good and create a world that is more just for all. The presentation of photos from the Willamette studio day and personal stories of our own campus allows individuals to see themselves and others within the context of the larger community to demonstrate that each individual belongs. Join us on April 7th at 7:30 pm in the Paulus Lecture Hall located in the law school building.','/e/6377',NULL,'2025-04-07 06:00:00+00','2025-01-24 21:36:46.234728+00','2025-01-24 21:36:46.234728+00','','John Paulus Lecture Hall','2025-04-07 06:00:00+00','2025-04-07 18:00:00+00'),
